    {
      "id": "PopularPost10243",
      "post_content": "This card is quite beneficial in certain situations. Having it become a creature is very easy, especially when played against aggro decks. But where the real usefulness comes from is the ability to have it withdraw back into an enchantment when it comes under the threat of getting killed. Burn spells, destroy instants, creature damage; none of it will work when you can turn him back into an enchantment for nothing. His only downside would be that if the opponent doesn't cast creatures often then hes not going to see play a lot but instead will be forced to do nothing as an enchantment. His other weakness is that he's only a 2/4, not really all that powerful. My solution to that problem would be to play this guy with [Doran, the Siege Tower](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doran, the Siege Tower) to give him a power boost (need I really inform most player of such an easy combo?).",
      "posted_by": "SavageBrain89",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost10243\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This card is quite beneficial in certain situations.  Having it become a creature is very easy, especially when played against aggro decks.  But where the real usefulness comes from is the ability to have it withdraw back into an enchantment when it comes under the threat of getting killed.  Burn spells, destroy instants, creature damage; none of it will work when you can turn him back into an enchantment for nothing.  His only downside would be that if the opponent doesn't cast creatures often then hes not going to see play a lot but instead will be forced to do nothing as an enchantment.  His other weakness is that he's only a 2/4, not really all that powerful.  My solution to that problem would be to play this guy with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doran, the Siege Tower\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doran, the Siege Tower\">Doran, the Siege Tower</a> to give him a power boost (need I really inform most player of such an easy combo?).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '10243'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy636\">SavageBrain89</span>\r\n                                (6/27/2009 5:55:28 PM)\r\n                    