    {
      "id": "PopularPost371130",
      "post_content": "With the advent of enchantment creatures in Theros, the oracle text on this one should be changed due to the fact that a permanent can now be a creature AND an enchantment at the same time. The second ability should now specify that it's no longer a creature when turned into an enchantment.   \n  \nIt should say:   \nWhen an opponent casts a creature spell, if Opal Acrolith is an enchantment, it becomes a 2/4 Guardian creature with \"0: End this effect.\". *(When you end this effect, it turns back into an enchantment and stops being a creature.)*",
      "posted_by": "acolyte_of_night",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost371130\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">With the advent of enchantment creatures in Theros, the oracle text on this one should be changed due to the fact that a permanent can now be a creature AND an enchantment at the same time. The second ability should now specify that it's no longer a creature when turned into an enchantment. <br/><br/>It should say: <br/>When an opponent casts a creature spell, if Opal Acrolith is an enchantment, it becomes a 2/4 Guardian creature with \"0: End this effect.\". <i>(When you end this effect, it turns back into an enchantment and stops being a creature.)</i></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '371130'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy82534\">acolyte_of_night</span>\r\n                                (4/19/2014 5:59:24 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars