      "post_content": "@acolyte\\_of\\_night: the reason that this is either a creature or enchantment but never both was never because enchantments and creatures are exclusive; its because both effects are replacements effects. [Blood Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blood Moon) prevents nonbasics from doing things other than tapping for {R} because it changes them into a Mountain, not into a Mountain *in addition to their other land types* (like [Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth)). Likewise, Opal Acrolith turns into a creature, not \"a creature in addition to its other types\" and back to an enchantment the same way.",
      "posted_by": "EvilDarkVoid",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost377760\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">@acolyte_of_night: the reason that this is either a creature or enchantment but never both was never because enchantments and creatures are exclusive; its because both effects are replacements effects. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blood Moon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blood Moon\">Blood Moon</a> prevents nonbasics from doing things other than tapping for {R} because it changes them into a Mountain, not into a Mountain <i>in addition to their other land types</i> (like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth\">Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth</a>). Likewise, Opal Acrolith turns into a creature, not \"a creature in addition to its other types\" and back to an enchantment the same way.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '377760'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy95215\">EvilDarkVoid</span>\r\n                                (6/1/2014 9:14:25 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<di